{
  "stem": "13198.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's what I had to do-- get all these children's knapsacks ready, my knapsack packed-- just the necessaries.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were all packed into a lorry, and driven off to a train in Amsterdam, and locked in carriages.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, after long, long hours, we arrived in the dark.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was in Germany that they'd got us to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When did I go to Westerbork?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, it was this castle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're right!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I've got in a muddle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've missed out the whole of Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I really can't remember it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These are all the very important people in Holland of Jewish origins.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You put it like that-- judges, lawyers, doctors, sort of that [FRENCH]-- schoolmasters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very long.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think about six months or something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't a bit nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I'd been very spoilt and had a nanny for my children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I was used to the English life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I suddenly was landed with three very naughty little boys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm not a bit of an authoritative person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody listened to me when I said, you mustn't do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I had a pretty hard life ruling my own children, which are the real little devils, they were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, she was arrested right in the beginning, when they were deported.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came one-- one night and took her out of her house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I heard that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, we weren't allowed to travel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I couldn't go and see her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just was told by somebody else, they've come and arrested your mother and taken her away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I heard no more from her, ever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my eldest sister was also taken with her husband.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
